Title: Jozi
Writer: Craig Freimond (screenplay), Craig Freimond (story), Robbie Thorpe (story)
Actors: Carl Beukes, Lionel Newton, Lindiwe Matshikiza, Nick Boraine
Plot: James is a successful comedy writer. There is only one small problem, he lives in Johannesburg and has completely and utterly lost his sense of humour.
